ary  Jacob Kent Langhorne Papers James L  Merritt letters Includes a letter written the day after the battle  J  Henry Reid Papers John E  Roller Papers Includes a letter from Peter Roller to his son  giving a civilian s account of the fighting in the valley  Andrew Stevenson Papers For additional collections  see the Civil War Manuscripts Guide  New Market Photographs Online Photographs Database Search for New Market cadets and related topics Institute Records Correspondence about the battle Report of Gen  Francis H  Smith  July 1864 Report of Col  Scott Shipp  Shipp led the cadets into battle Orders May 1864 Related Information Hunter s Raid  June 1864  VMI Arsenal   Ordnance  1859 1864 Archives Home Digital Collections Archives Online Catalog Quick Info  FAQs Civil War   New Market Battle of New Market Ghost Cadet Home Letters   Diaries VMI s Civil War Generals Timeline  VMI Popular Questions Hunter s Raid Home John Brown Execution Stonewall Jackson Genealogy   Alumni Photos   Portraits Letters  Diaries  Manuscripts Digital Exhibits Home Military Oral History VMI Records Records Management About the Archives Mary Laura Kludy Archives Assistant Ph   540  464 7516 Fax   540  464 7089 archives vmi edu Preston Library Lexington  Virginia 24450 Hours   Visitor Info Archives Home Digital Collections Archives Online Catalog Quick Info  FAQs Civil War   New Market Battle of New Market Ghost Cadet Home Letters   Diaries VMI s Civil War Generals Timeline  VMI Popular Questions Hunter s Raid Home John Brown Execution Stonewall Jackson Genealogy   Alumni Photos   Portraits Letters  Diaries  Manuscripts Digital Exhibits Home Military Oral History VMI Records Records Management About the Archives Mary Laura Kludy Archives Assistant Ph   540  464 7516 Fax   540  464 7089 archives vmi edu Preston Library Lexington  Virginia 24450 Hours   Visitor Info Archives Home Digital Collections Archives Online Catalog Quick Info  FAQs Civil War   New Market Battle of New Market Ghost Cadet